nodemon ./bin/www

export NODE_ENV=production
nodemon ./bin/www
these two lines above are for running production environment: production doesn't show the error trace.

1. ssh -i node_keypair.pem ubuntu@ec2-54-173-35-59.compute-1.amazonaws.com

* If warning sign occur telling you that the key is unprotected then you need to change permission 
chmod 400 node_keypair.pem

To run node on ec2:
nohup node ./bin/www &

Check PID on ubuntu:
ps -ef